d to the Goods and Services Act, 2017<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Hands-on knowledge of Compliance related to the Companies Act, 2013<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Assisting the manager with special projects as necessary;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Provide reporting and research of accounting issues as needed;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Reconciliation of Bank statements, Debtor reconciliation, Vendor reconciliation;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What we are Looking for: &#8211;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>The candidate should be able to work well with others on a team while also being able to work independently on assigned tasks and campaigns. Must be capable of taking on additional responsibilities and growth opportunities.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ability to establish and maintain a positive and professional working relationship with all individuals; listens carefully and understands various points of view.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Must be flexible both in time and responsibility with the willingness to grow alongside a rapidly growing organization.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Job Types: Full-time, Regular \/ Permanent<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Salary: \u20b9550,000.00 &#8211; \u20b9750,000.00 per year<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Schedule:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Day shift<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Supplemental pay types:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Yearly bonus<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Job Description Requirements: Job responsibilities: What we are Looking for: &#8211; Job Types: Full-time, Regular \/ Permanent Salary: \u20b9550,000.00 &#8211; \u20b9750,000.00 per year Schedule: Supplemental pay types:<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"template":"","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"default","site-content-layout":"","ast-site-content-layout":"","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"","ast-main-header-display":"","ast-hfb-above-header-display":"","ast-hfb-below-